<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. I lunggil gilo thim nuoia,
 Van hinna chi kituh hi;
 Pak ding leh gah ngei dinga,
 Enkawl dingin thupiek I hiu;
 Hinna Lallukhuk lawh dingin.

[V2]
 Lalpa Isu Thagau hun sawlin,
 Nanga dinga pak gimlim hung hithei dingin;
 Na Lallukhuk hawihna dingin,
 Ka ginnau hih thiengtho in.

[V3]
 2. I gam nam mawl genthei sungah,
 Chang bang damna chanchin pha;
 Pak ding leh gah ngei dinga,
 Enkawl dinga thupiek I hiu;
 Felna Lallukhuk lawh dingin.

[V4]
 3. Lalpa Thagau lo a hin chu,
 Chitna, thiemna leh sanna;
 Phatna dan leh felna dan,
 Lunggil a hung pak ding ngei chu;
 Ei nang gitloh gal a suok thei.

[V5]
 4. Hehpihnan kawt lien tak a hawng,
 Van Lal nasepna dingin;
 Tui vatkhat leh thingphel khat,
 Thil muhsit um tincheng hawhi;
 Van gam go a suohsak theihna'n.</lyrics>
<title>Hinna Chi</title>
<author>Thangngur</author>
<hymn_number>109</hymn_number>
</song>